</div>\n    </nav>\n    <section class=\"block block--colored block-page-header about about--business\">\n      <h1 class=\"block-page-header__heading\">Businesses</h1>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--light block--instructions--preview about about--business\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <p>\n              Shiftly makes it easy to connect with reliable student\n              workers—without the hassle of hiring. Whether you need help for a\n              busy night or ongoing weekly support, we've designed the process\n              to be fast, flexible, and low-risk.\n            </p>\n          </header>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--light block--instructions about about--business\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <h2 class=\"block__heading\">How it Works:</h2>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">1. submit a shift</h3>\n            <p>Tell us when and where you need help. You'll provide:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Date, time, and location of the shift</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Hourly wage (must meet or exceed state minimum wage)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Basic job description (ex: packaging food, dishwashing, cashier,\n                etc.)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Point of contact for the day of the shift\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              We'll make your shift available to our pool of nearby student\n              workers right away.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">2. students apply</h3>\n            <p>Students see your shift in real time and apply to claim it.</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                You will be able to see their profile and rating before\n                confirming\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                You can reject applicants for free as long as it is 24 hours\n                prior to the shift\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Shifts are first-come, first-served–but you're always in control\n              of who works.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">3. after the shift</h3>\n            <p>Once the shift is completed, we'll ask you to:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Rate the student on punctuality, work ethic, and professionalism\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Confirm the shift was completed as expected\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Leave feedback to help them grow (optional)\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Shifts are first-come, first-served–but you're always in control\n              of who works.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">4. pay monthly</h3>\n            <p>\n              We take care of payments to the student directly. You'll receive\n              an invoice once a month with:\n            </p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                A breakdown of hours worked and students who completed shifts\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                A single payment total to keep bookkeeping simple\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              No need to handle payments or taxes–Shiftly manages all that on\n              your behalf.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--colored about about--business\">\n      <div class=\"block__text\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n          <div class=\"block__text\">\n            <header class=\"block__header\">\n              <h2>Why Shiftly Benefits Businesses</h2>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n              <ul class=\"list\">\n                <li class=\"list__item\">\n                  Flexible scheduling–send us shifts as needed\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">Last minute staffing</li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">Access to dependable student workers</li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">Simple invoicing and no hidden fees</li>\n              </ul>\n              <p>\n                Whether you're looking for extra help on a busy Friday night or\n                filling a few weekly shifts, Shiftly is your fast,\n                student-powered staffing solution.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__penguin\">\n            <img src=\"/253245c6102f71845525e657952ff217.svg\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--dark block--bottom\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Students</h4>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"list\">\n            <a href=\"/a06f72b3e226a32ee6e99456d3af971a.html\">How it Works</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">FAQs</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb